497
00:26:21,300 --> 00:26:23,600
SO WHAT'S MORE AFFORDABLE THAN A PROMISE?

498
00:26:23,900 --> 00:26:24,600
LOOK, EDIE--

499
00:26:24,700 --> 00:26:26,100
I'M DOING THIS FOR YOU.

500
