655
00:33:30,100 --> 00:33:32,200
I GET IT.
YOU'RE UNCOMFORTABLE.

656
00:33:32,600 --> 00:33:36,100
JUST GO. I'M FINE.

657
00:33:38,600 --> 00:33:40,300
I'M FINE.

