THAT ENCOURAGING STORY.

663
00:34:05,300 --> 00:34:07,200
I'M NOT FINISHED.

664
00:34:09,800 --> 00:34:11,599
THOSE LAST WEEKS,

665
00:34:11,600 --> 00:34:15,200
